<a-band id="intro" double>
    <a-card class="content">
        <p class="extra"><strong>We partner with organizations large and small to build sustainable, accessible front-end infrastructure that scales.</strong></p>
        <p>We've managed complex technical initiatives that resulted in highly profitable and impactful outcomes. From scaling a barebones design system into a mature enterprise-level solution to leading a multi-million dollar government contracts, we've seen it all. No task is too big or too small when you have the right partner with the right mindset and expertise.</p>
        <p>Founded in 2025, we combine deep technical expertise in design systems and web standards with proven program management capabilities. Whether you need someone to architect your component library, lead a complex digital transformation with lots of moving parts, or bridge the gap between design, engineering, and business strategy—we deliver results.</p>
        <p>We believe the best technology is invisible—it empowers teams to do their best work without getting in the way. We specialize in creating infrastructure, establishing workflows, and leading initiatives that make complex problems feel manageable. We leverage AI-augmented engineering workflows to accelerate development and improve quality while reducing costs and can empower your teams to do the same.</p>
    </a-card>
</a-band>

